{"attributes":{"kind":"function","backlinks":[],"methods":[{"symbol_id":"Pkg.PlatformEngines.verify","module_id":"Pkg.PlatformEngines","file":"PlatformEngines.jl","line":553,"signature":"(::Signature)"}],"package_id":"Pkg@1.8.2","title":"verify","symbol_id":"Pkg.PlatformEngines.verify","exported":true,"module_id":"Pkg.PlatformEngines"},"tag":"documentation","children":[{"attributes":{"symbol":"Pkg.PlatformEngines.verify","line":534,"module":"Pkg.PlatformEngines","file":"PlatformEngines.jl"},"tag":"docstring","children":[{"attributes":{},"tag":"md","children":[{"attributes":{"lang":""},"tag":"codeblock","children":["verify(path::AbstractString, hash::AbstractString;\n       verbose::Bool = false, report_cache_status::Bool = false)\n"],"type":"node"},{"attributes":{},"tag":"p","children":["Given a file ",{"attributes":{},"tag":"code","children":["path"],"type":"node"}," and a ",{"attributes":{},"tag":"code","children":["hash"],"type":"node"},", calculate the SHA256 of the file and compare it to ",{"attributes":{},"tag":"code","children":["hash"],"type":"node"},".  This method caches verification results in a ",{"attributes":{},"tag":"code","children":["\"$(path).sha256\""],"type":"node"}," file to accelerate reverification of files that have been previously verified. If no ",{"attributes":{},"tag":"code","children":["\".sha256\""],"type":"node"}," file exists, a full verification will be done and the file will be created, with the calculated hash being stored within the ",{"attributes":{},"tag":"code","children":["\".sha256\""],"type":"node"}," file.  If a ",{"attributes":{},"tag":"code","children":["\".sha256\""],"type":"node"}," file does exist, its contents are checked to ensure that the hash contained within matches the given ",{"attributes":{},"tag":"code","children":["hash"],"type":"node"}," parameter, and its modification time shows that the file located at ",{"attributes":{},"tag":"code","children":["path"],"type":"node"}," has not been modified since the last